Comment: It is a easy game for beginners to get used to the % operator.

Goal
* Please format "N" and "K" as [[variables]].

Input
* Please revise the format of all lines like this:
<<Line ?>>: (variable type) [[variable name]], which (description)
e.g.
<<Line 1>>: An integer [[N]], which represents the number of elements in the list.

(The last line number description would be <<Next [[N]] lines>>.)

Output
* Please format "K" as a [[variable]].

Constraints
* Please format "N" and "K" as [[variables]].

* N and K is much less than 100,000 in all the cases. Please revise the upper bound and/or the cases and ensure that the range is evenly covered in the cases.

Cases
* Each pair of test and validator should be *similar* but *not the same*. Please revise the cases accordingly.

Thanks.
Could you please write a reason for your approval, instead of just the word "approved"? Thanks.
